'''[[Homecoming]] [[King]]'''
#(''US'') In [[college]]s and [[high school]]s, a young [[man]], chosen by his [[peer]]s, to "[[reign]]" over the [[traditional]] activities associated with the Homecoming [[American football|football]] game. Often chosen to reign alongside a [[Homecoming Queen]].

